<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ هُدْبَةُ بن خَشْرمٍ الْعُذْرِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١ - صَبُورٌ عَلَى مَكْرُوهِ مَا يَجْشَمُ الْفَتَى ... وَمُرٌّ إِذَا تُبْغَى الْمَرَارَةُ مُمْقِرُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣٠)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ قَيْسُ بنُ الْخَطِيمِ الأَوْسِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الخفيف)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١ - فِيِهِمُ لِلْمُلايِنيِنَ أَنَاةٌ ... وَطِمَاحٌ إِذَا يُرَادُ الطِّمَاحُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣١)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وقَالَ الأَسْوَدُ بنُ يَعْفَرَ النَّهْشَلِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١ - وَإِنِّي لَشَهْمٌ حِينَ تُبْغَى شَهيمَتِي ... وَصَعْبٌ قِيَادِي لَمْ تَرُضْنِي الْمَقَاذِعُ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣٢)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ جَذْلُ بنُ أَشْمَطَ:</span> <span class="c2">(المنسرح)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>١ - مُرٌّ إِذَا مَا هَزَزْتَ أَثْلَتَهُ ... وَهْوَ زُلالٌ كَأَنَّهُ عَسَلُ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣٣)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ حَسَّانُ بنُ ثَابِتٍ الأَنصَارِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>١ - وَإِنِّي لَحُلْوٌ تَعْتَرِينِي مَرَارَةٌ ... وَإِنِّي لَتَرَّاكٌ لِمَا لَمْ أُعَوَّدِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>